Class Professor

java.lang.Object
project332.Person
project332.User
project332.Professor
public class Professor extends User
Represents a professor in the library system. A professor is a type of user with specific attributes like rank. This class extends the User class, inheriting general user attributes and behaviors while adding specific details relevant to professors.
